data.description: Welcome to this amazing home in the highly sought-after Ensenada at Tres Lagos subdivision! This property offers 5 spacious bedrooms, a bonus room, an office space, and 3 and a half luxurious bathrooms (including a Jack & Jill bathroom). The 2-car garage is roomy and convenient. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the impressive two-story ceilings in the grand foyer, family room, and office, allowing plenty of natural light to fill the home. The Chef's Kitchen features stunning granite countertops, a gas stove top, a large pantry, and ample storage space. In addition to the formal dining room, there is also an eat-in-dining area. The Primary Suite, located on the first floor, provides easy access to the covered patio. The en-suite bathroom is a dream, with separate vanities, a shower, and a relaxing soaking bathtub. The bonus room offers flexibility for your needs, whether it's a playroom, home gym, or media room. With the spacious backyard, this home provides plenty of room.
